As a kog'maw main, I personally love when they make skins for my mains but even I think he has quite a few to choose from, correct me if I'm wrong but I think this most recent skin makes him tied with teemo and jax for most skins? This is his 10th skin, while some of the older champs like zilean have only 6. I love that riot is making skins and I'm not saying to cancel the skin just because he has alot of them, but maybe share the love and let some other mains feel the joy of seeing that new skin in the patch notes.

From,
A Kog main  {{champion:96}}

